description.plain: Country Music trio made up of Miranda Lambert, Ashley Monroe, & Angaleena Presley.  The trio gave it’s debut performance on April 4, 2011 on the Academy of Country Music’s Girls' Night Out: Superstar Women of Country on CBS.  The women gave themselves the nicknames ‘Lonestar Annie’ (Lambert); ‘Hippie Annie’ (Monroe); and ‘Holler Annie’ (Presley).  Songs they are known for are “Hell on Heels”, “Hush Hush”, and “I Feel a Sin Comin' On”.

songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1: Ashley Monroe]
I picked a good day for a recreational Percocet
I've got an itch to just get high
I'm in the middle of the worst of it
These are the best years of my life

[Verse 2: Angaleena Presley]
I've got the hankering for intellectual emptiness
I've got the need to ease my mind
I'll watch some re-runs on the TV set
These are the best years of my life

[Chorus: Miranda Lambert]
I was looking forward to
Staying here forever
'Cause you asked me to
Didn't think that I could do better
So I settled down
In this ten-cent town
It's about to break me

[Verse 3: Miranda Lambert]
I'm gonna mix a drink and try to drown this worthlessness
Call Mom and tell her I'm alright
Well he don't love me but he ain't gone yet
These are the best years of my life

[Instrumental]
